=Dharmaraksa 竺法護 (c. 230-304)=
buddhist monk, born at Dunhuang, Yuezhi ethnic origins. Also called "Bodhisattva of Dunhuang"
==Sources==
* [[高僧傳]] Entry No. 8 (--> transl. Robert Shih, 1968, pp.33-37)
